{"tid":1157240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 食品廠男工遭機器切斷手 傷勢嚴重送院搶救","createTime":"2019-05-16T06:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80f22082dc6b6bc2aa33f4ecafd6e08a5a3a5789","tid":1157240,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2802985/org/f0b5e1e91533f9ffa6e7011e00a534e8.jpg/T86-6o-TlDz264pxHXNbBIpTNY7X06KSsWd6xbFnesU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2802985%2Forg%2Ff0b5e1e91533f9ffa6e7011e00a534e8.jpg%2FT86-6o-TlDz264pxHXNbBIpTNY7X06KSsWd6xbFnesU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d1976c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（16日）早上10時許，葵涌永業街21號永業工廠大廈樓上一間食品廠，一名男工人於廠房內操作攪拌機時，意外切傷右手。食品廠的工友立即報警，男事主清醒被送往瑪嘉烈醫院，他連同斷手送院治理。警方正調查意外原因，案件暫列工業意外處理。據了解，男傷者右手與前臂分離，傷勢嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/329532/%E6%96%B7%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E5%82%B7-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%B7%E5%B7%A5%E9%81%AD%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E5%88%87%E6%96%B7%E6%89%8B-%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%A2%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%90%B6%E6%95%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F329532%2F%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%2588%2587%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%2589%258B-%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2595%2591&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdfz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e0d7a1cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/329532/%E6%96%B7%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E5%82%B7-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%B7%E5%B7%A5%E9%81%AD%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E5%88%8